    "services.cta.title": "Ready to automate this?", "services.cta.body": "Book a free consultation and we'll show you exactly how this would work for your business.",
    "services.7.title": "Conversational AI", "services.7.desc": "Enterprise-grade voice and chat interfaces that understand context across every channel, in every language you operate in.",
    "services.7.subtitle": "Natural, multilingual conversation at enterprise scale.",
    "services.7.intro": "Beyond a single chatbot: we build conversational AI layers that work consistently across voice, web chat, WhatsApp and IVR — understanding context, switching languages, and handing off to the right system or person.",
