    "services.7.f5": "Continuous tuning based on real conversations",
    "services.7.example": "For example: a municipal client replaced a phone-tree IVR with a conversational assistant that understands resident requests in multiple languages and routes them directly to the right department.",
    "services.8.title": "Intelligent Document Processing", "services.8.desc": "Automatically read, classify and extract data from contracts, invoices and forms — at the volume logistics and government teams actually deal with.",
    "services.8.subtitle": "Turn document piles into structured, usable data.",
