    "services.8.f5": "Built to handle high-volume, mixed-format documents",
    "services.8.example": "For example: a logistics client used to have a team manually keying in customs and shipping documents. We built a pipeline that extracts and validates the data automatically, cutting processing time from days to minutes.",
    "services.9.title": "Managed Services", "services.9.desc": "Ongoing monitoring, support and optimization once your automations are live — so performance never quietly degrades.",
