    "about.label": "About us", "about.title": "Built in Rotterdam. Built for European business.",
    "about.p1": "Automatix FCZ was founded in 2026 by Ruslan and Fadil — automation engineers and AI specialists based in the Netherlands. We help logistics, industry, government and professional-services organizations replace fragmented systems with practical, well-integrated AI automation — not hype, not vendor lock-in.",
